`InstanceConfig.getTags()` should never return `null`. Are you using a different Helix version?
Here's the Helix code:
```
  public List<String> getTags() {
    List<String> tags = getRecord().getListField(InstanceConfigProperty.TAG_LIST.toString());
    if (tags == null) {
      tags = new ArrayList<String>(0);
    }
    return tags;
  }
```

