Thanks for pointing out! The purpose of this PR is to address an issue when the helix tag for minion host is missing, and we suspect that it's due to an NPE from this part of code. @amrishlal we can remove the null check for the returned reference of getTags, while a null check is needed for instanceConfig. Please include that into this PR.
